Nupponen, sp. nov. (BIN: BOLD:ADY7738, 4.49%).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F8CE5865B478604BB98DABB86E2A2EB6" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" type="remarks">
<paragraph id="289CB93574C6D292E67DFB25C40B20FC" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Remarks.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="D7C6FE3D2E4BA524F81EEB463CF42E85" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">
Female unknown. Based on COI maximum likelihood phylogeny, the South American taxa 
<taxonomicName id="5E8BA9B4AEE210E845087D77F29D0143" authorityName="Nupponen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris salinasgrandensis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="salinasgrandensis">
<emphasis id="7A823BE8BE1B63D1D6BB390277F7AE12" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris salinasgrandensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="97EBF352B1556F4F02AB1AD67A64CC33" authorityName="Nupponen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris furciphallella" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="furciphallella">
<emphasis id="8FBD359AC383D064A8E38576720E0431" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris furciphallella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="20708DDF3F109BE9ED619E5FC6469F79" authorityName="Nupponen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris manchaoensis" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="manchaoensis">
<emphasis id="6DB139C9F328539214E3A0A640AC84F3" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris manchaoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="9CBF19D885F63F68FD986A89153CA7AA" authorityName="Nupponen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris angustivalvella" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angustivalvella">
<emphasis id="399D939D5B9DDA0E30BC8EEC219045E0" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris angustivalvella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="274BDFF47449E6FA5685EE349BD5DB4F" authorityName="Nupponen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris directiphallella" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="directiphallella">
<emphasis id="65AA4F062DEDE2E678AB4313423C2685" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris directiphallella</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
