<taxonomicName id="39F80A8C3368617AE075D22FB089B936" authorityName="Nupponen 1 &amp; Sihvonen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="F7516FE6C319706ED23AE59C63109E8A" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
on BOLD (Suppl. material 2). We classify these taxa in 
<taxonomicName id="4ACA622DE68E5A39DC47E4FF0F63FCC3" authorityName="Nupponen 1 &amp; Sihvonen" authorityYear="2022" class="Insecta" family="Scythrididae" genus="Scythris" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Scythris" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="0" pageNumber="19" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="F2C9D096A4A737660CE721957B499DA2" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="19">Scythris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
